{"tid":486315,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[佛徒也要過耶誕]你們要到全世界去，向眾生轉法輪!","createTime":"2017-12-01T17:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T03:08:00.000Z","uid":31001,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb4625b11550a372ea25acf55e44a22effd87a1","tid":486315,"uid":31001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"各位善信好!<br />\n<br />\n耶誕又到了，不知各善信們又會怎樣過?<br />\n<br />\n貧道則因早前定慧寺事件，被趕去寺院，<br />\n户口被凍結，現閉關修行。<br />\n禪定其間，貧尼驚覺眾生們都會為耶誕而普天同慶，<br />\n然而，貧尼認為佛門弟子亦有權感受節日氣氛，<br />\n故此貧尼設計出一張佛門既耶誕祝福卡。<br />\n<br />\n正面:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/010732_e73bddb4a29adf2a64eb7afe977edcbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F010732_e73bddb4a29adf2a64eb7afe977edcbb.jpg&h=3e0edc7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背面:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/010811_6e732b25581f45a9bcd47ab60f4039c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F010811_6e732b25581f45a9bcd47ab60f4039c9.jpg&h=f518932a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連同金色信封乙個<br />\n<br />\n願眾生都能覺悟，感受我佛既慈悲精神。<br />\n宏正法轉法輪的人，他們的腳蹤何等慈悲！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如善信們欲此耶誕祝福卡，請填寫以下google form：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/QwBStCJx2zOQWojB2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FQwBStCJx2zOQWojB2&d=y6AftZrosRa1SWwQALRMabr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=71b2cec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/QwBStCJx2zOQWojB2</a><br />\n另外，因早前定慧寺事件，貧尼已身無分文，<br />\n希望善信能隨心布施少量香油，以支付耶誕卡的印刷費與郵費。<br />\n<br />\n我不以正覺為恥，這正覺是宇宙的真理，要渡一切相信的。<br />\n沙門所結的果子就是菩提，有智慧的，必能得人。<br />\n願各位早聞正法，早證菩提!<br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛"},{"pid":"f26851ac8cf02e647d76b1c9995f6840a47b5078","tid":486315,"uid":31001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"高清版<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/01211